    Extract the features of the end edge of each phylogenetic flow

    pf_end_features.Rd

    Extract the features of the end edge of each phylogenetic flow

    Usage

    pf_end_features(x)

    Arguments

    x

    A pfc object

    Value

    A numeric vector of the features of the end edge of each phylogenetic flow
